                  </persName>
            . I have known him fourteen years; I never heard any ill of him till this unhappy affair.</p>
               <p>Q. Is he a single man or has he a family?</p>
               <p>Perry. I don't know.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t17721209-26-person306">
