                  </persName>
            . I have known him a great many years; I never heard any harm of him.</p>
               <p>Q. Do you know whether he is a single or married man?</p>
               <p>Perry. Single.</p>
               <p>Q. Do you know whether he was in work at time?</p>
               <p>Perry. No.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t17721209-26-person307">
