            . It have known him upwards of seventeen years; I never heard a bad thing of him before this.</p>
               <p>Q. Do you know where he worked last?</p>
               <p>Arbuthnot. No.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t17721209-26-person308">
                  Rees
                   Davis
               <interp inst="t17721209-26-person308" type="surname" value="Davis"></interp>
