            . I have known him between eight and nine years; I never knew any harm of him.</p>
               <p>Q. Do you know where he has worked?</p>
               <p>Davis. I am not acquainted with his master.</p>
               <p>
                  <xptr type="pageFacsimile" doc="177212090016"></xptr>
            
